<tr>
<th>Born</th>
<td>16 August 1913<span style="display:none">(<span class="bday">1913-08-16</span>)</span><br />
<a href="/wiki/Brest,_Belarus" title="Brest, Belarus">Brest</a>, then <a href="/wiki/Russian_Empire" title="Russian Empire">Russian Empire</a>, now <a href="/wiki/Belarus" title="Belarus">Belarus</a></td>
